Administrator, Software Engineer, SQA.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Project Track|guide:_ShowProjectTrackPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click *Sprint* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Sprint Detials" Report|guide:PtShowSprintDetailsReportActionService].
* Enter valid input.
* Click "PDF Report" button from tool bar .
* System will show confirmation message of download.
* Actor clicks "Ok" button.
* Download *Sprint Details* Report in PDF Format.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Download Sprint Details" privilege.
* Rules of Searching:
{table}
*Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Rules*
[Project|guide:GetDropDownPtProjectTagLibActionService] | Drop Down List | Numeric | Required
[Sprint|guide:PtGetSprintListByProjectIdActionService] | Drop Down List | Numeric | Required
Owner| Checkbox | Boolean | Optional
{table}


h4. Process:
* To get *Sprint Details* Report in PDF Format "Click Here":sprintDetails.pdf
* Download the report as PDF format.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** PDF Report will successfully download to user's computer.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].